commit.message:
Revert "ui: workaround for buggy window behaviour under wayland gnome"

This reverts commit dd90ef1ec10715f64c8b7955b2ab81ec22285879.
ui: workaround for buggy window behaviour under wayland gnome
gap: fix pulse output to work better with pipewire server
restore color theme saving after FOX 1.7.81 change
extra: remove old python helper scripts
cfox: workaround for possible broken XDrawRectangle
Improvements to Secure Sockets and allow SSL connections to other ports besides 443
ap_socket: fix implementation with updated FXIO
taglib: stop using deprecated api in 1.12
remove support for long gone LyricWikia
flac: add support for 32 bit samples introduced in FLAC 1.4
